{"tid":220531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵 侵 表 明 不 會 再 與 蔡 英 文 通 電 話","createTime":"2017-04-28T04:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T12:01:53.000Z","uid":23707,"like":9,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc587b51fd0202536680e2f66989103dae52861","tid":220531,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b69e984e80bb5b342a633be1777b8960adc5bab","tid":220531,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:09:57.000Z","msg":"from NOW news"},{"pid":"6c607b6c0671749cbc52afbd6f97304b41ceb795","tid":220531,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:10:42.000Z","msg":"whatsapp n Skype<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c25d9ab382a1145e3a80a4e06c649b3427734da","tid":220531,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:10:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=219306&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D219306%26home%3D1&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c2c5c467\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D219306%26home%3D1&h=ee066b92\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=219306&amp;home=1</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普拒跟蔡英文再通電話<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普接受路透社專訪，表明不會再跟台灣的蔡英文總統通電話，原因是他不想為國家主席習近平製造麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮接受訪問，透露自己不想再跟蔡英文通電話的原因，是不想為難習近平。<br />\n<br />\n他讚揚習近平是偉大的領袖，指彼此之間已建立良好的個人關係，又感到習近平正盡一切努力協助美國解決北韓問題，因此不想為對方添煩添亂，要談也會先跟習近平談。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普當選總統後曾接聽蔡英文賀電，惹北京不滿。特朗普二月時表明華府恪守一個中國原則。<br />\n<br />\n對於蔡英文表示不排除向美國買F-35戰機，特朗普說沒有收到通知，他會跟美國人民從長計議後才作出決定。"},{"pid":"3c2fafe28562db1d474ee8c41b79e36d0c44a7d7","tid":220531,"uid":45471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:11:06.000Z","msg":"親自見面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4399ca4e62293728d66702cce8965c9170293c","tid":220531,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:11:44.000Z","msg":"連侵侵都變埋習大棋子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83edbf5bd3bac0095c452ae90524a313e4cd8cc8","tid":220531,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"Trump反中反共 會幫香港建國"},{"pid":"86f482339c4985d7b4e36d4a377d59f468d174ae","tid":220531,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"美國要同台灣政府/總統對話, 唔一定要通呢個直線電話<br />\n根本就大把渠道, 又係中共啲小學雞要面既行為<br />\n如果呢一個其中因素可以換取到中共不會軍事支援朝鮮, 真係無所謂"},{"pid":"e1bc564877cb4b2db9b3c2b5f9c5a8406f4a98e9","tid":220531,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連侵侵都變埋習大棋子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依局棋似係美國對北泡，邊個先係棋子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e75518939ebd5e6a04ebbe6199e6321bb06ddcc","tid":220531,"uid":20158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"台灣狗dum春未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7909bc614b44abe713b0907744644394c8143d05","tid":220531,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:18:45.000Z","msg":"商人治國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}